      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to get this beauty into a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, and you won\u2019t find a single blemish anywhere. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one. Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
