    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This S54-powered icon features six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, both meticulously serviced for razor-sharp throttle response and linear power delivery to the 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced and the rod bearings replaced with treated shells\u2014proactively addressing the platform's vital mechanical requirements. The suspension retains its original kinematics and bushing integrity, ensuring telepathic steering rack feedback. With flawless paint depth and an interior devoid of bolster wear, this example is mechanically and aesthetically indistinguishable from its showroom debut.",
      "price": 48500.0,
