      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and garage-kept since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with a professional ceramic coating that highlights the flawless body lines\u2014absolutely zero dings, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state, featuring supple leather that still retains its factory aroma and a dashboard that has been shielded from all UV exposure. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with the precision of a new car. With a complete, documented service history from authorized dealers and extremely low mileage, this car represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. It drives as beautifully as it looks, offering a tight, responsive experience that perfectly mirrors its original delivery day.",
